<H3> <TI>   PDS Chief: Party To Be Represented in Next Bundestag </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    PDS Chief: Party To Be Represented in Next Bundestag </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU1306114694 Hamburg DPA in German 0928 GMT 13 Jun 94--FOR 
