<H3> <TI>   Environment Minister Johansson Resigns </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Environment Minister Johansson Resigns </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Oresund Bridge Plan Cited </H4>

<F P=102> LD1606131394 Helsinki Suomen Yleisradio Network in Swedish 
1300 GMT 16 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1606131394 </F>
<F P=104>  Helsinki Suomen Yleisradio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Swedish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Olof Johansson, Swedish environment minister and 
chairman of the Center Party, has resigned from the government. 
Environment Minister Johansson resigned after Prime Minister 
Carl Bildt decided that the Government of Sweden will approve 
the construction of the Oresund bridge. It is not known yet 
whether the other Center Party ministers in the government will 
resign. 

</TEXT>

