<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    NATO Holds Air Force Exercise in Europe </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR1506114494 Brussels BELGA Database in French 1609 GMT 14 
Jun 94 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> BR1506114494 </F>
<F P=104>  Brussels BELGA Database </F>
<F P=105>  French </F>


