<H3> <TI>   Finnish Trade Minister on EU Membership </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Finnish Trade Minister on EU Membership </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PM1406121094 London FINANCIAL TIMES in English 14 Jun 94 p 
12 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

