<F P=106> [Article signed J-LO: "CSV To Hold Coalition Negotiations </F>
With the LSAP Following the Parliamentary Elections on 12 June 
-- Party Chairman Jean-Claude Juncker Heads the CSV's 
Eight-Strong Coalition Delegation"] 
  [Excerpts] After nearly three hours of consultations at an 
extraordinary meeting in the metropolitan "Carrefour" [episcopal 
conference center], the national council of the Christian Social 
People's Party (CSV) resolved yesterday evening, with an 
overwhelming majority (there were only two abstentions, made for 
