<H3> <TI>   Explains Reasons for Resignation </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Explains Reasons for Resignation </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1906201194 Paris France-2 Television in French 1830 GMT 19 
